Use the following programs to rename files in a given directory


Open the file and specify the text and directory via the macros and the run the files as listed below.

Find and Replace Text:

./Batch Find Replace.py             Test script and see filenames to be updated
./Batch Find Replace.py -w          Write out and replace filenames

Append or Prepend to each filename:
./Batch Prepend Append.py -w

Adjust numbers within given text for each file:
./Adjust File Numbers.py -w
